oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Winton Home, Martel, TN
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: unknown
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Home built by Rev. John and Arabella Cunningham Winton, Martel, TN. (Near Lenoir City, Loudon County, TN). Their descendant Horace Mann and his wife Frances and their family lived in the home from 1912-1918.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Houses;
